RawLine: NEAR_02001_04,雖然你幫忙破解了聖地機關，但兩人終究沒從洞內參透什麼。於是李見義決心只好繼續鑽研武藝，期待自己有朝一日能參透藏墨劍法，再興三派。,虽然你帮忙破解了圣地机关，但两人终究没从洞内参透什么。于是李见义决心只好继续钻研武艺，期待自己有朝一日能参透藏墨剑法，再兴三派。

Items.mt: Although you helped to break the sacred mechanism, the two of them did not learn anything from the cave after all. The two of you have helped to crack the sacred ground mechanism, but the two of you have not learned anything from the cave. So Li Jianyi is determined to continue to study martial arts, hoping that one day he will be able to learn the Hidden Ink Sword Technique and revitalize the three schools.
